Name: Dancing with the Dreams Stage 1
Desc: When an enemy target's Weakness is Broken, add <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak></color> hits to "Memory Turbulence"'s Hits Per Action. If the target is an Elite enemy or higher, then additionally add <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak></color> hits, up to a max increase of <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak></color> hits.\nAt the start of every Cycle, every hit by the "Memory Turbulence" deals 1 instance of a set amount of DMG to random enemy targets, and the Hits Per Action is not reset.

Challenge.Name: Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Have no downed characters
